symf.name: PAGE_EXECUTE
symf.desc: enables execute access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_EXECUTE_READ
symf.desc: enables execute or read-only access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_EXECUTE_READWRITE
symf.desc: enables execute, read-only, or read/write access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_EXECUTE_WRITECOPY
symf.desc: enables execute, read-only, or copy-on-write access to the mapped view of a file mapping object

symf.name: PAGE_NOACCESS
symf.desc: disables all access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_READONLY
symf.desc: enables read-only access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_READWRITE
symf.desc: enables read-only or read/write access to the committed region of pages

symf.name: PAGE_WRITECOPY
symf.desc: enables read-only or copy-on-write access to a mapped view of a file mapping object
